              alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <p></p>
            <p>Asia is a very popular place to travel to. For the most part it
              is extremely cheap and has lots of activities to do while
              backpacking. Because of how large and diverse Asia is, it offers
              many activies. These activities can range from leisure, adventure
              based and sightseeing.</p>
