          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <p></p>
            <p>Thailand is a beautiful country with lots of things to do. It is
              very cheap. Young travellers often visit here because of the price
              and the laidback attitude the locals have. Below is a suggested
              place to visit while in Thailand</p>
            <p></p>
            <b>Hoi An</b>
            <p></p>
            <b>Price of activity:</b> $ <br>
            <b>Name of hotel/hostel:</b> Sala Hotel <br>
            <b>price of Hotel/hostel:</b> $$ <br>
            <b>Safety of location: </b> Very safe <br>
            <p></p>
            <p><b>Notes:</b> Hoi An is a very beautiful place. It is very cheap
              and there is lots to do near by the listed hotel. The town has
              many old buildings and statues to see. The bars are extremely
              cheap and there are beautiful beaches near by.</p>
            <p><b><br>
              </b></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
