              alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <p><br>
              Vietnam is another very popular place for young travellers to
              visit. There is a lot of history in Vietnam as well as beautiful
              beaches and sights. Below is a suggested activity to do while in
              Vietnam.</p>
            <p></p>
            <b>Overnight Boat Ride in Halong Bay</b>
            <p></p>
            <b>Price of activity:</b> $$$ <br>
            <b>Name of hotel/hostel:</b> Halong Party Cruise <br>
            <b>price of Hotel/hostel:</b> $$$ <br>
            <b>Safety of location: </b> Very safe <br>
            <p></p>
            <p><b>Notes:</b> The boat cruise is 2 days. It takes you along
              different islands in Halong Bay. The food is included in price.
              There are many activities to do on the islands as well as many
              beaches to lounge at. Kayaking is recommended.</p>
            <p><b><br>
              </b></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
