            <p><br>
              Bali is a small island with beautiful sights. Many travellers go
              to Bali to see these sights. The beaches hold very clear blue
              water and white sand. below is a suggested activity to when in
              Bali.</p>
            <p></p>
            <b>Hike and relax</b>
            <p></p>
            <b>Price of activity:</b> $ <br>
            <b>Name of hotel/hostel:</b>Air BNB <br>
            <b>price of Hotel/hostel:</b> $ <br>
            <b>Safety of location: </b> Very safe<br>
            <p></p>
            <p><b>Notes:</b> As mentioned before, Bali is very beautiful. There
              are hostels in Bali, however it is cheaper and safer to stay in an
              Air BNB. While in Bali, suggested activities include hiking and
              lounging on the beach. There are many places to hike and many
              beaches all over the island.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
